Test webapp to send mail. It uses MyFaces 2.0 and Spring Framework.

Configured for gmail smpt (requires access for less secure apps in Google Account).

Run with maven jetty plugin : mvn jetty:run -Dmail.user=<mail.user> -Dmail.password=<mail.password>

Properties mail.user and mail.password are required for authentication. Set them on the command line or with a configuration file.